latestMessage.message:
Hi, all fantastic Telavox people! 💃

It's time to reveal why we should all dress up on the second night of the kickoff! We are, of course, going on a gala - the Telavox Awards! 🏆

The awards gala will highlight extraordinary efforts from Telavoxers since the last kickoff and celebrate together. We will celebrate both individual and team efforts. There are fantastic achievements and people all over Telavox worth celebrating! ⭐

As usual, it works like this:
1. Telavoxers nominate colleagues in the defined awards categories with motivation.
2. The Telavox Group Management team read all nominations and selected winners in each category based on nominations.
3. Winners are presented at the gala.
4. All nominations (anonymously) are being sent out to each person after the gala. We never miss an opportunity to spread the love. 

The gala includes the following awards: 
💚 Culture Ambassador 
⭐️ Leader of the Year 
🏆 Business Result Champion 
👯‍♀️ Best Team Effort 
💡 Innovation Master 
🦄 Telavox Guru 
🚀 Rockstar Rookie 
👑 Customer Hero

➡️➡️➡️ NOMINATE COLLAUGES HERE: https://telavox.typeform.com/to/zHcjlPMA ⬅️⬅️⬅️ 
We close nominations by September 11th. 

Find everything you need to know about the awards and nominations here: https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1p1Vug-yXHLA-yIHxelHlNQqkEg9aXMKRo0pByTXclIQ/edit?usp=sharing 

Questions? kickoff@telavox.com  

Have a fantastic day! 💃
Kickoff Party Crew & Telavox Management Team
